<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Castleridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Castleridge was established back in 1980. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The community is bounded by the Falconridge Boulevard on the east, Mcknight Boulevard on the south, 44 Street E on the west and 64 Avenue N on the north.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Castleridge include a variety of residential units ranging from single-family detached homes to bungalows and even apartment condominiums that are readily available at an average price of $370,000.</p>
        </div>
